{% extends "narrative_agent/base_draft.j2" %}

{% block task_description %}writing the complete narrative text for a chapter{% endblock %}

{% block focus_section %}
Chapter: {{ chapter_number }}
Plot point focus: {{ plot_point_focus }}
{% endblock %}

{% block instructions %}
1. Write the ENTIRE text for Chapter {{ chapter_number }}.
2. Bring the plot point focus to life as on-page action, dialogue, and interiority.
3. Maintain continuity with the Hybrid Context.
4. Output ONLY the chapter text. No chapter header, no title, no analysis, no code fences.
5. Length: at least {{ min_length }} characters.
{% endblock %}
